	// summary:
	//		a Mixin to handle mouse or touch events for a focus-less menu
	//		Abstract methods that must be defined externally:
	//
	//		- onClick: item was chosen (mousedown somewhere on the menu and mouseup somewhere on the menu)
	// tags:
	//		private

